<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Welcome</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f3f4f6; padding: 30px; margin: 0;">
    <div style="max-width: 620px; margin: auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">

      <!-- Header -->
      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #1d4ed8); padding: 25px; text-align: center;">
        <h1 style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 28px; margin: 0; letter-spacing: 1px;">
          Real Estate App
        </h1>
      </div>

      <!-- Body -->
      <div style="padding: 30px;">
        <h2 style="color: #111827; font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 18px; text-align: center;">
           Welcome, <%= firstName %>!
        </h2>

        <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 20px;">
          We’re excited to have you join the <b>Real Estate App</b> community. Your account has been
          successfully created, and you’re now ready to explore the latest listings, connect with verified
          agents, and manage your property interests with ease.
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 25px;">
          Whether you’re buying, selling, or renting, our platform is designed to make your real estate journey
          smoother and more transparent. We're here to help you find a place you’ll love calling home.
        </p>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 35px 0;">
          <a href="http://localhost:5173/login"
            style="background: #2563eb; color: white; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 8px;
                   text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;
                   display: inline-block; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);">
            Login to Your Account
          </a>
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top: 25px; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; text-align: center; line-height: 1.6;">
          If you did not sign up for this account, please ignore this email.  
          For any questions or support, feel free to reach out to our team at 
          <a href="mailto:support@realestateapp.com" style="color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none;">support@realestateapp.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div style="background: #f9fafb; padding: 18px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
        <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #9ca3af; margin: 0;">
          &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Real Estate App. All rights reserved.  
          <br />
          You are receiving this email because you created an account on Real Estate App.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
